      },
      {
        "Language": "ENG",
        "Name": "A Sinking Feeling",
        "Client": "Newbie Captain",
        "Description": "After getting my first ship, I was\r\ntasked with ferrying knights to\r\nthe Jungle, but Hermitaur and\r\nVelociprey roam the shores!\r\nI don\u0027t like the look of this...\r\nI JUST became captain! I\u0027m not\r\nready to go down with the ship!",
        "Target": "Slay a total of 15 Hermitaur or Velociprey",
        "Fail": "Reward hits 0, or time expires"
      },
      {
        "Language": "FRE",
        "Name": "Un v\u00E9ritable naufrage",
        "Client": "Capitaine en herbe",
        "Description": "J\u0027ai accept\u00E9 de transporter des\r\nchevaliers jusqu\u0027\u00E0 la Jungle\r\ndans mon nouveau bateau, mais\r\nil y a des Hermitaurs\r\net des Velociprey partout !\r\nJ\u0027ai peur pour mon bateau !\r\nFais quelque chose !",
        "Target": "Tuer un total de 15 Hermitaur\r\nou Velociprey",
        "Fail": "Prime \u00E0 0/Temps expir\u00E9"
      },
      {
        "Language": "ITA",
        "Name": "Rimorchiatore d\u0027avanguardia",
        "Client": "Capitano amante delle navi",
        "Description": "Finalmente sono capitano e con\r\nil mio vascello ho traghettato\r\ni cavalieri nella giungla, ma\r\nci sono Hermitaur e Velociprey\r\nsulla costa. Se la mia barca\r\nvenisse danneggiata, sarebbe\r\nuna tragedia. Fa\u0027 qualcosa!",
        "Target": "Uccidi 15 Hermitaur o Velociprey\r\nin totale",
        "Fail": "Premio a zero o tempo scaduto"
      },
      {
        "Language": "GER",
        "Name": "Fahrige F\u00E4hre",
        "Client": "Kapit\u00E4n Neuanbord",
        "Description": "Ich wurde beauftragt, Ritter in\r\nden Dschungel zu schippern,\r\naber an den Ufern treiben sich\r\nHermitauren und Velociprey rum.\r\nIch bin gerade erst Kapit\u00E4n\r\ngeworden! Ich m\u00F6chte nicht mit\r\nmeiner ersten F\u00E4hre untergehen!",
        "Target": "Erlege insgesamt 15 Hermitauren\r\noder Velociprey.",
        "Fail": "Belohnung auf 0 oder Zeit\r\nl\u00E4uft ab."
      },
      {
        "Language": "SPA",
        "Name": "Tocado y hundido",
        "Client": "Capit\u00E1n novato",
        "Description": "Desde que consegu\u00ED mi barco\r\nme dedico a llevar caballeros\r\na la Jungla, \u00A1pero la costa est\u00E1\r\nllena de Hermitaur y Velociprey!\r\nAcabo de llegar a capit\u00E1n... \u00A1no\r\nquiero hundirme ya con mi barco!",
